General Information
===================

libbuddy is a simple C library for manage i-Buddy devices.

Installation
============

./configure
make
make install

* Example to troubleshoot permissions on Debian: 

1. configure udev rules on /etc/udev/rules.d/51-ibuddy.rules :

SUBSYSTEMS=="usb", ATTRS{idVendor}=="1130", ATTRS{idProduct}=="00??", GROUP="games", SYMLINK+="ibuddy%n"

2. add user to group "games":

sudo gpasswd -a $USER games

tested on Debian 6.0 (Squeeze)

Dependencies
============

- libusb-1.0

